        "PALADIN_TYPHOONUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "作为圣骑士在台风或更高难度完成游戏或抹除自己。\n<color=#8888>(台风难度需要安装 Starstorm 2 模组)</color>",
        "PALADIN_TYPHOONUNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "圣骑士:大师精通",
