        "PALADIN_POISONUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "作为圣骑士,与堕落女神签订契约。",
        "PALADIN_POISONUNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "她的门徒",
        "PALADIN_LIGHTNINGSPEARUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "愉快的合作",
        "PALADIN_LIGHTNINGSPEARUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "作为圣骑士,用皇家电容攻击一个敌人。 <color=#c11>仅主机。</color>",
        "PALADIN_LIGHTNINGSPEARUNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "愉快的合作",
